reviews.review_text: Good Recording, Good Show This is one of many great shows here on Archive dot org. I am kind of spoiled rotten by the Aug 6 1971 show, which is my very favorite so far. So I will give this one 4 stars for the great recording and song list. Try the Hollywood Palladium show I mentioned from Aug 6 1971, they were really ON that night. The Palladium show the night before is good also. I'm 64 years old, by the way, and from Missouri. Happy listening !
